<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-5810] Wrong installation path for static MSVC libs.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-5810</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-5109&quot; title=&quot;Misc CMake improvements&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;THRIFT-5109&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;THRIFT-5109&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; the LIB_INSTALL_DIR for MSVC libs chanaged from lib/ to bin/ regardless if shared or static libraries were built.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;While for shared MSVC libraries, installation to bin/ folder is correct, the commonly used installation path of static libraries (not only for MSVC) is the lib/ folder. The changes made in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-5109&quot; title=&quot;Misc CMake improvements&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;THRIFT-5109&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;THRIFT-5109&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; do not distinguish between static and shared MSVC libs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Static MSVC libraries should be installed into the lib/ folder, as it has been done in 0.13.0.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
